\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a replay\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"the epic race\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"incredible finish\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"Tatjana Smith\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coming into the 100m Olympic breaststroke final on Monday night, Tatjana Smith was the clear favourite, but she touched and turned at the 50m mark trailing in fourth place.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 100m Olympic breaststroke\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday night\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 475}, {\"ngram\": \"Tatjana Smith\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50m mark\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"fourth place\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, a stunning late surge in the final 20m enabled her to touch the wall first in1.05.28toclaim South Africa's first gold medalat theParis Games2024.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999980636858, \"rank\": 1.93613764332558e-09, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stunning late surge\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the final 20m\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"Games2024\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think anyone can explain it,\\\" she stated afterwards.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Like I said last night, for me the emotions were really because it took a village to get me to where I am.\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"a village\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know they would have been proud even if I did not have a medal.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was really for them; I swam for everyone that's been there for me and believed with me.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was for our country as well, our hashtag for [Team SA's campaign] is 'For my Country'.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0608605153622154e-18, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"our hashtag\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"my Country\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it really is, it's just to inspire someone at home, for them to know they are not disqualified from the race and to know that they could potentially be an Olympic champion.\\\"\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith's own Olympics tally has now grown to three, with two golds and a silver.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith's own Olympics tally\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"two golds\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One more will see her equal Chad le Clos on four, the most of any South African Olympian.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chad le Clos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\"}, {\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999992518317483, \"rank\": 7.481686305932091e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her attention will next turn to defending her gold in the 200m.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her attention\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"her gold\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been an incredible journey over the last few years as Smith once admitted she was considering walking away from the pool.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an incredible journey\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes when the expectations get too much you lose the fun and joy out of competing, and that definitely played a role in the last two years,\\\" she said during an interview last year.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the expectations\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"the fun\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"the last two years\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's definitely been tough.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You think there is a lot of expectations but it's mostly your own.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You always think people will be disappointed if you do not pull out the same performances as before.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"the same performances\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You just have to give your best; you can not always be at your complete best.\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think any athlete has run, swam PBs left, right and centre every time they compete.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any athlete\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"swam PBs\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can never always have the perfect race and I think it was one of the challenges after the Olympics - it's impossible for me not to expect a lot from myself. \\\"\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the perfect race\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenges\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2353}, {\